channel.title: Zeneko- Individual [Chill] (remixable)
channel.description:
Hey all you lovely people!
I made a new track, and revealed my first other alias! “Zeneko” is gonna be my alias for any chill tracks, ambient included. Check it out:
https://soundcloud.com/lunarlexxx/zeneko-individual
It does have some oriental influences. :slight_smile:
Here are the stems just for the heck of it, I’d like to see what kind of Remixes you guys make. I’ll repost any remixes on my SC!
https://app.auxy.co/projects/zr35FOgw-ZiTlMkpUIdI8g==
Feedback would be very appreciated.
